,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"反被消化 陰功"},{"pid":"3a354c48a622bb66e471ce76777d1bcaa45a01ea","tid":527853,"uid":156341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203ae4b520ebe055d2c1b9d18fe839e8f2316dbb","tid":527853,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"有7成咁多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38e4417b1ca8e825ab4f61aa25f0609c606a0f6","tid":527853,"uid":161821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱睇完隔離廣州嗰個post好撚驚"},{"pid":"22b85663fa8e4cf7bf4f800b5fe76520f2c5e4c4","tid":527853,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"如果同政治無關點解廣州今時今日會搞成咁呀？"},{"pid":"4a26453174ae8940fe93a18ba68d0dc4c5f919c5","tid":527853,"uid":19485,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"而家班新移民真係好撚大牌，死唔講廣東話<br />\n仲要人就佢講普通話黎同佢對答<br />\n我做學校，成日打電話比家長<br />\n基本上十個總有3-4個人打比佢佢要求我講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有時講兩句會轉返做廣東話<br />\n憑乜你黎香港讀書要我就你講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你去美國讀書要求啲老師唔講美文講普通話就你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ec89335807f038a75baeca6deff727a94e0133","tid":527853,"uid":166438,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote